results.description:
Plan Your Tasks is a productivity tool that allows you to capture your ideas and duties in one place. 
Manage everything you have to do while working with many different tasks!

Easy task management - create, organize, and prioritize tasks;
- Set notifications;
- Add comments;
- Sort tasks by categories;
- Track due dates.

New approach to agenda
- Build-in calendar;
- Coherent tutorial mode;
- Magic Trackpad 2 support.

Capture all your flash ideas and duties in the calendar and manage your to dos while working with many tasks more effectively.


